    dc:creator "Ahmad, Ayashaa; Sharma, K. K.; Vidyarthi, A. S.; Ramani, R." ;
    dc:date "2013" ;
    dc:title "Three new species of Kerria (Hemiptera: Sternorrhyncha: Coccoidea: Tachardiidae), a redesciption of K. yunnanensis Ou & Hong, and a revised key to species of Kerria" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.215577>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.215584> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.215577>
    dc:description "FIGURES 1 – 6. Tests of Kerria spp. 1, K. manipurensis Ahmad & Ramamurthy, sp. nov., adult females, ex Malvaviscus penduliflorus; 2, K. maduraiensis Ahmad & Ramamurthy, sp. nov., adult females, ex Albizia saman; 3, K. thrissurensis Ahmad & Ramamurthy, sp. nov., adult females, ex Amherstia nobilis; 4 – 6, K. manipurensis Ahmad & Ramamurthy, sp. nov., K. maduraiensis Ahmad & Ramamurthy, sp. nov., and K. thrissurensis Ahmad & Ramamurthy, sp. nov., adult female after removal of test and cleared in KOH." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/215577/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.215584>
    dc:description "FIGURES 57 – 65. Kerria yunnanensis Ou & Hong. 57, whole mount. 58, anal tubercle. 59, dorsal spine. 60, single duct of dorsal duct cluster with dorsal seta. 61, brachia with anterior spiracle. 62, marginal duct cluster. 62 a, single duct magnified. 63, antenna. 64, ventral seta. 65, posterior spiracle." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/215584/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

